Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:11.60,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, čuo sam glasine na putu od Lubinhajgena.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.65,Dialogue,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, da, strašno je.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.94,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li to pričate o čarobnjaku koji se pojavio na novom putu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.30,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čuo sam tu priču.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.10,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da može da prizove vukove i manipuliše njima po svojoj volji.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.51,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oni napadaju putnike kako bi pili njihovu krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.73,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije valjda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:32.58,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Istina je. Bolje je da budete oprezni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:36.41,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo sam čuo od jednog crkvenjaka dok sam bio u Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:40.50,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čitav karavan je napadnut pre dve nedelje.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.87,Dialogue,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, strašno... Nije li strašno?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.10,Dialogue,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toliko se plašim da ću još da pijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zapamtiću tu priču.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.32,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moliću se, za tebe, da taj čarobnjak nije žensko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.68,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čini se da tebe žene mogu lako da prevare,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.52,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}da ne pominjemo kako se ponašaš posle toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.33,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Od kako se ono desilo počeo si da piješ više alkohola.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:14.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U skoro svakoj krčmi koju smo posetili se pričalo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.88,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}o Medio trgovini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.43,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Muškarci su stvarno glupa stvorenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izvini što sam glup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:29.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vuk i prava ravnoteža
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.54,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakav dosadan grad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.52,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Krčma se zatvara prerano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, ovim mestom upravlja administracija pobožnog grada Lubinhajgena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.19,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budi zahvalna što uopšte postoji krčma za putnike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:46.06,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li ovaj grad ne interesuje ništa sem vođenja pokornog života i svakodnevnih molitvi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:52.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo mesto je najbolje poznato po podužim, uspavljujućim besedama o crkvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije mi uopšte jasno šta je tu zabavno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:01.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Krećemo za Lubinhajgen čim prodam biber i kupim nova dobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.90,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je li to veliko mesto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.57,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, veće od Patsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Više je grad nego mesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Živahno je i ima mnogo radnji na otvorenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.47,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoće li biti jabuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:13.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam siguran da će imati išta kvraljivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:16.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je sezona za konzervirano voće.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.51,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Konzervirano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne mislim na ukiseljena dobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Voće očuvano u medu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.77,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I to ne samo jabuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kruške očuvane u medu su takođe ukusne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A od skoro ima i breskvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Breskve...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:36.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sitno seckane breskve se slažu unutar bureta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:39.82,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prvoklasni proizvodi sadrže i smokve i badem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:45.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto se med sipa na breskve, dodaje se đumbir. Onda ih tako čuvaju po dva meseca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:53.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Njihov sladak ukus koji ti ispunjava usta kao da nije sa ovog sveta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:56.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije začuđujuće da je čak crkva jednom razmatrala i da ih zabrani.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, balaviš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.29,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti me ne lažeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:09.40,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne lažem, ali obično su rezervisane za bogate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, retkost su na tržištu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-Šta ćeš učiniti ako se budu prodavale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.06,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-U redu, kupiću ti ih.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali samo malo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je obećanje, razumeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej, slušaš li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:26.67,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo odmah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde idemo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.00,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde drugde?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo do gostionice po naša kola i onda idemo do te neke trgovine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:39.55,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probudićemo upravitelja, prodati biber po dobroj ceni, i krenuti ka Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čekaj malo. U ovo doba noći?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.79,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možda se prodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.35,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To bi bila totalna katastrofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:49.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šanse da ih uopšte ne bude su veće nego da se rasprodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.61,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Breskve i med, u to je teško poverovati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.15,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne može biti istina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali to je samo ako budemo imali sreće, razumeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.62,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mada,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.37,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne bi mi smetale ni kruške.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:09.88,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pastorova propoved je istinski dirnula naša srca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:14.34,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je stvarno bio blagoslov od Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:21.05,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Njegove reči su nas podstakle da stremimo većim visinama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:26.32,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, malo sam odlutao. Hajde da se vratimo poslu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.80,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hajde.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:31.14,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta imate da nam ponudite danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.16,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biber, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.46,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako ste znali?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.54,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zbog mirisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Impresivno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.77,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije, nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.80,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dođe vam prirodno kada se bavite ovim poslom dugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:54.52,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da nemate kojim slučajem vagu pri sebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:02.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemam, ali imam vere u Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.95,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, baš nemam sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.23,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tražnja za biberom se značajno povećala u zadnje vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:18.74,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da ste došli samo nedelju dana ranije, mogao sam da ga kupim jeftinije.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.61,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mora da sam došao u pravo vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:26.55,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svakako. Hajde onda da krenemo sa merenjem bibera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.21,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:32.89,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Trebaće nam papir i mastilo. Izvinite me na trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.50,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.38,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Žedna sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.53,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budi strpljiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.68,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćete malo vode?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.19,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imam i vina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.66,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, mogu li da dobijem vode?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.57,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nema problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.58,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To mu dođe srazmerno sa četrdeset i pet mera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:12.89,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koje je poreklo ovog bibera?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biber je iz Ramapate iz Kraljevstva Lidon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.88,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Milone trgovina je obavila uvoz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:24.50,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ramapata je poznata po svojim začinima,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.50,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}i ova potvrda izgleda ispravno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:34.46,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta kažete na jedan Lumione zlatnik po meri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koliki je kurs za Lumione zlatnike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.41,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li želite da budete isplaćeni u Torenijevim srebrnjacima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:47.76,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kurs je trideset sedam i pet šestina Toreni srebrnjaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.64,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toliko ćemo da vam platimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prihvatam ponudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.24,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, onda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.92,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta nije u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.64,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vrti mi se u glavi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.10,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Da li ste dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.74,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.18,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li se osećate bolje?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:19.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, hvala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.70,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Verovatno ste se umorili od dugog putovanja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.40,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doneću vam malo mleka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gospodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:32.25,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da je prizor pred mojim očima nakrivljen iz nekog razloga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako izgleda vašim očima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.90,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne, svakako nije nakrivljen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.92,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne bi trebalo da je moguće, ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.71,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vidim nešto što ne bi trebalo da je moguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:02.34,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da mi je dato vino umesto vode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.57,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije li tako, gospodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:13.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kao što kaže izreka, "Što je krčma pijanija, to je krčmar trezniji."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sada razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:19.46,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Očigledno je da čovek mora ostati trezan da bi uspešno poslovao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:22.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da sam i ja bio malo opijen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.27,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Verovatno ću zaboraviti neke od stvari koje sam video i čuo ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:30.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali, poznato je da pijanice znaju da nepromišljeno izlaju stvari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.30,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:38.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Platićete mi ugovorenu cenu, zatim ono što ste nameravali da zaradite na meni, i...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.58,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dozvolićete mi da kupim na kredit dva puta više dobara nego što smo se dogovorili.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.76,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duplo? To je previše!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, šteta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.19,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da počinjem da se treznim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hajde da razgovaramo o robi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:56.79,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto je suma poveća, recimo da mi platite visoko kvalitetnim oklopima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.10,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi, kažete?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je pouzdana roba koja će zagarantovano obezbediti profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:07.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moći ću da otplatim svoje dugove sa tom robom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siguran sam da skladištite dosta robe za prodaju u Lubinhajgenu, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.64,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi, kažete?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.62,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno ste u dobrim odnosima sa drugim trgovcima iz Lubinhajgenu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.56,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spreman sam da poremetim balans tako što ću prodati dobra njima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.69,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta kažete na to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Puno vam hvala.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:30.89,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Molim vas da što pre obezbedite robu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želeo bih da krenem za Lubinhajgen što je pre moguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.41,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.61,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A procena robe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:41.33,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepustiću to vama. Ja imam vere u Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siroti čovek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.37,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iznenađen sam da si primetila.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:01.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moj izgled, moja pamet i krzno na mom repu ne gube od nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.07,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isto važi i za moj sluh i vid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.32,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Primetila sam čim smo kročili ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.45,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta to treba da znači?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta ti je, odjednom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:16.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iskustvo vodi samouverenosti, a to ponekad može da bude smrtonosno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar nisi ništa naučio iz incidenta sa Kloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.32,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U potpunosti si u pravu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Samo činiš stvari gorim kada si tako mrzovoljan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.65,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uči iz iskustva i nastavi dalje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulje?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.51,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, čujem da je dobro za timarenje mog repa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:46.12,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možeš li mi kupiti malo kada stignemo do sledećeg grada?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:53.59,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jesi li ikada razmišljala o ceni odeće koju nosiš, rezervne odeće, češlja,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:58.49,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}o putnim troškovima, hrani i računima za sve piće koje popiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu su i lični porezi koje plaćamo pri ulasku u grad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.70,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li je prosta matematika previše za tebe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.19,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umem da sabiram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:10.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobra sam i u oduzimanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako je tako, saberi koliko mi duguješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako si mudra koliko tvrdiš da jesi, trebalo bi da znaš na šta ciljam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.14,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.02,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znam da ćeš mi kupiti još.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:28.94,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čak i mudri vuk kao što si ti postane jadan kada je pijan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:32.15,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam pijana, znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budalo! Šta to radiš...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šalim se.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.32,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.61,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoj da me potcenjuješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:47.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Misliš li da nisam primetila kada si dobio više nego što si očekivao,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}iskoristivši slabost onog trgovca?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.08,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćeš li mi kupiti ulje?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:57.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li znaš koliko mi još novca duguješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.28,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sto četrdeset srebrnjaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siguran sam da znaš da je to pravo malo bogatstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako očekuješ da ti povrh toga još kupujem neke tričarije?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:10.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je? Da li toliko želiš da ti isplatim svoj dug?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na -  ra -  vno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.75,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znači stvarno si tako mislio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na šta misliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:25.38,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, kada otplatim dugove, slobodna sam da činim kako želim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:30.27,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, dobro. Trebalo bi što pre da ti platim i da se zaputim ka severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ionako sam se navikla da budem sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.54,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam još odredio rok za otplatu duga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.82,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biće u redu ako mi platiš u celosti pre nego što stignemo do šuma na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.28,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li se slažeš sa time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:53.11,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, sigurno ću moći da ti vratitm dug dok stignemo do šuma na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:15:01.78,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Osim toga, razmišljam da ti dodam i kamatu na ono što ti dugujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:07.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drugim rečima, što ti više dugujem, više ćeš profitirati. U redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.52,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulje, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:16.07,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da. Možeš ga uračunati u moj dug, pa mi kupi malo, hoćeš li?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:23.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dogovoreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.37,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.86,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakav divan dan za doterivanje.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:54.63,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nego, zar nisi dobio priličan popust na ova dobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.29,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pomislih da možda nije najbolja ideja da živim na grbači siromašnog putujućeg trgovca.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.24,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi su roba koja se najbrže prodaje u Lubinhajgenu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.31,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali ima i dosta trgovaca koji ih prodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.29,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu nema mnogo prilika za zaradu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tako da nije ni bitno da li sam dobio popust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.96,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali zar nećeš zaraditi pošto si kupio veliku količinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.22,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, pokriću bar troškove za ulje.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.45,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je dobro čuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:29.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali kad pogledaš, začini su jako dobri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.42,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probao si ih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:32.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoj da me spuštaš na tvoj nivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.90,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Govorim o njihovoj profitabilnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.64,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto ne trguješ začinima opet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.90,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prodajna cena oklopa je ista bilo u Lubinhajgenu ili u Porosonu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.99,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na začinima bih izgubio zbog poreza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.22,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda ništa od toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:51.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kada bih na drugoj robi zarađivao kao na začinima, brzo bih skupio pare da otvorim radnju.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.92,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar nema nečega na čemu bi mogao tako zaraditi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:58.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na primer, dijamanti i zlato bi se verovatno dobro prodavali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takve stvari nisu previše profitabilne u Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Porezi su isuviše veliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:14.42,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uvezeno zlato koje ne pripada odabranoj grupi trgovaca je podložno visokim porezima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iz tog razloga ne vredi trgovati njime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:20.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto su neki trgovci izuzeti od poreza?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imaju veze sa crkvom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:28.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kada tamo uvezu zlatne poluge, na njih se utiska Sveti žig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:31.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takvo zlato biva blagosloveno prvoklasnom cenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U zamenu za to, crkva dobija izdašne priloge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.23,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kvarno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.67,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato su izuzetno strogi po pitanju krijumčarenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prokrijumčarena dobra se prodaju po duplo većim cenama,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali uz njih ide veliki rizik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:53.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato uglavnom nema budala koje bi se okušale u tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.17,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar je tako teško sakriti nešto kao što je zlato?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tamošnje kontrole tovara su prilično temeljne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.25,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta bude kada te uhvate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.39,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U najgorem slučaju, odseku ti ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.59,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jednostavno nije vredno toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:15.72,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, tvoj posao ide solidno. Nema ništa loše u tome da postepeno napreduješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:21.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Upravo. A ko je taj što troši moj, s mukom zarađen, novac?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.25,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bolje da budete pažljivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.94,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da su došli plaćenici sa severa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Plaćenici?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.01,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.57,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kretanje dalje ovim putem bi onda bilo samoubistvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, oni spaze svoj plen brže od orla
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:57.22,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}i otimaju sve od vrednosti, ne ostavljajući ništa za sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.56,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A i naoružani su dugim kopljima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čak i za mene je to više muke nego koristi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.97,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iznenađen sam što su sišli ovako daleko na jug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.96,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kao i trgovci, oni uvek delaju u svom najboljem interesu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, nema svrhe o tome pričati ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:20.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, idemo za Lubinhajgen novim putem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne plašiš se valjda neznabožačkih čarobnjaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.36,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:28.75,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da na ovom putu ima čopora vukova.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oni su manji problem od ljudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sa njima bar mogu da se sporazumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda ću tebi prepustiti pregovore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.43,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali baš nema nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.17,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da glasine brzo putuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:58.12,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dosadno. Ja ću da dremnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćeš li moći da osetiš vukove i ako zaspiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naravno da hoću!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bilo bi gadno da nas okruže.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Previše se brineš.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:11.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Što se tiče nas životinja, nema neke razlike da li spavamo ili ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.28,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ljudi su previše ranjivi kada spavaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To nije baš ubedljivo kada kaže neko ko hrče u snu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.62,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, nisi baš toliko glasna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.82,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažem ti da ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.49,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Razumem, razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uopšte ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.36,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažem ti da razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:34.87,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:39.02,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Odavde ću prepustiti priču tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko je ispred nas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ljudi koje mrzim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čarobnjak o kom smo pričali?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.03,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovce?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.38,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je li to taj čarobnjak?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.68,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je to bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je ritual kada sretneš pastira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:38.47,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bar znamo da nije čarobnjak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sam putujući trgovac, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je moja saputnica, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želim da zamolim pastira kog sam sreo vođen božjom rukom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.16,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}da se pomoli za našu bezbednost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.45,Dialogue,Norah,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biće mi drago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sedam jabuka na veštičinom drvetu,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sa sedam semenki da zasadiš u meni.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:37.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U proleće mi je narasla magična pesma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I onda, skakućući okolo, pevala sam je svima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:48.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gledala sam svet kroz oči jabuke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:53.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,i isekla sebi deo sunčane pite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plesala sam sa kikiriki leptirovima
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:02.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,dok nije došlo vreme i reklo mi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:05.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,da kažem zdravo ali mašem zbogom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:10.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiljadu šećernih zvezda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.81,0:23:15.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stavi ih u teglu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:18.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I onda zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:21.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O, zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:25.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja sam mali vuk u devojci,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:26.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti kažeš
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:31.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pređoh iz juna u maj."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:35.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O, zviždući po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajde da zviždućemo po svetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:52.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sledeća epizoda, "Vuk i pastirovo stado".
